Package org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.placeholder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachedPlaceholder
    A cached placeholder will store the value of the placeholder for each online player.
    So if you replace the cached placeholder, you won't get the newest data immediately.
    By default, the cached placeholder will renew every 10 seconds.
    FixedPlaceholder
    A fixed placeholder will store the value of the placeholder for each online player.
    So if you replace the fixed placeholder, you will never get the newer data.
    Placeholder
    Represents a placeholder implementation.
    Warning: If you replace the placeholder, you will have the newest data so there is a problem with performance.
    Recommend: Uses FixedPlaceholder or CachedPlaceholder instead.
    PlaceholderAPI
    A class helps you to manage placeholders
